description: A funny skill with random challenges for breaking the ice and getting to know people at parties or social events. Includes self-introducing, pairing, drinking and many more tasks! Ideally, make a circle and just ask Ice breaker for your next challenge, following a clockwise direction. Let the party begin!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Ice Breaker for a challenge.
Alexa, ask Ice Breaker what should I do.
name: Ice Breaker
shortDescription: Break the ice with this party skill!
